blog.name: uphereintheopenair
blog.title: i didn’t wanna believe my feelings for you 🌸

summary: Dan Howell Came Out and I will never be over it
body:
Dan Howell Came Out and I will never be over it

Okay so I have a lot of feelings about this so I’m gonna try to keep it as clear and concise as I can. I can now die happy knowing that one of my favourite YouTuber’s (as I predicted and hoped) is gay. I know that may sound overdramatic a little but I have watched them both for so long and I’ve seen them grow into the lovely people that they are now and I’m just so goddamn proud of them ❤️ Dan is SO GOD DAMN BRAVE AND A FREAKEN GENUIS 🌈 putting that much time and effort into a coming out video not only talking about your struggles, but also talking about issues in the community that he wasn’t particularly struggling with is amazing, very inclusive, educational, and just honestly a good reminder for us all to be excepting. Real talk though what gets me is that this whole time they were together being in love in secret sharing little moments, being just a normal couple all while we all had no idea…but wish it was happening BUT IT WAS THE WHOLE TIME 😭❤️ and honestly I realize Dan said that they want to keep their private life private and that’s fine but I just need to hear him say that “Phil is my boyfriend” or something like that because I honestly think I’m still dreaming. Also can we talk about how now in the future they will be making videos together and they’ll just lean over and kiss each other on the cheek or grab each other‘s hand or something and I can’t even handle the thought of that being our reality 2019 IS NOW MY FAVOURITE YEAR AND NOTHING WILL EVER CHANGE THAT. I cannot wait for Phils coming out video because I’m curious about how Dan has helped him through his life and through his struggles 💞 Phil Lester is a GOD DAMN DELIGHT! AND ACTUAL RAY OF SUNSHINE ☀️ hearing dan talk about Phil in the way we always dream he would…was so fucking precious…it honestly made me see why Dan loves him so much. and also I’m sorry are they going to get married in 2022??? Possibly get a dog? move into an actual house??? I’m honestly so excited for whatever the future is going to come for them and I wish them the best ✨ Tbh I don’t care what they do as long as they love each other with every fiber if their being! I swear to God I’m gonna be like 80 and my kids and be like “mommy what was the best moment of your life?” and I’m gonna be like “On June 13, 2019… when Dan Howell came out and him and Phil Lester started living their lives like couple without hiding there truths like what they always wanted since they were 18” 😭💘 Thanks for coming to my TED Talk @2:00am… I’ve never posted one of these before sorry if it’s crap 😂
